text:
The rate per day in June was 400 usd per night. For these money you get: 
1. Fee of 3 dollars for item of luggage for storage;
2. No room service
3. Dated room
4. No breakfast included. They charge you 38 usd for very poor continental breakfast (no hot items);
5. In the restaurant they include service charge of 18% to the bill and ask for tips after that;
6. Small food kiosk near receipt does not charge purchases to the room;
7. They do not pick up laundry from your room. You need to bring it down yourself to the reception. They literally left bag of dirty clothes on my bed.
8. Reception is hardly reachable by phone.
